The ANC's NEC is meeting this weekend in Irene. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa has stated the ANC is a united party. The president was attending an education conference on the East Rand, where he told reporters the ANC NEC meeting went very well. READ: Ramaphosa dares detractors at NEC meeting Ramaphosa said, "within the ANC NEC we doing very well... we had fantastic discussions. "We are united, so don't fear."